snippet.title: For Madman Only - Main Theme [GAME soundtrack]
snippet.description:
Main theme of 2D platform indie game "For Madman Only".
The official link to the game: https://sparrowinthefield.itch.io/for-madman-only

Author of the game: Dorota Wróblewska
Music: Michael Wroblevsky

https://dorotawroblewska.artstation.com
https://www.facebook.com/di.wroblewska/


WroblevskyElectronicStudio 
Master: Adam Wroblevsky

**************************
If You liked it please subscribe our channel to hear more of our pieces. You can also visit our websites (links below). We would be happy to hear your opinion - you can leave a comment or contact us via mail. We hope that You enjoyed the time spent with the music performed by us specially for You. Visit us again and don't forget to give us a "thumb up"!!

Website: https://wroblevsky-wroblevsky.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Wroblevsky.and.Wroblevsky/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/wroblevsky.wroblevsky/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/WWroblevsky
